        <abstract>
            <p>Asks JVC to ascertain the age at which merino rams develop horns, and whether they grow faster or more slowly than in other breeds of sheep in which both sexes have horns.</p> 
<p>Asks how JVC’s translation [of <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>] has sold.</p> 
